<tal:layout define="columns1 default">
<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>
    <metal:heading fill-slot="pageheading">
      <h1>Help us improve</h1>
    </metal:heading>
    <div metal:fill-slot="main">
      <p>
        Launchpad is a work in progress, and we welcome your feedback on how
        to make it better.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            Got general questions or suggestions? Mail
            <a
              href="http://lists.canonical.com/mailman/listinfo/launchpad-users"
            >the Launchpad users mailing list</a>, or
            <a href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#launchpad">join us on IRC</a>
            (network <code>irc.freenode.net</code>,
            channel <code>#launchpad</code>).
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Found a bug in Launchpad?
            Check that it&#8217;s reported in the Malone bug tracker.
            Report bugs about:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="/malone/+bugs">Malone itself</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/rosetta/+bugs">Rosetta</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/soyuz/+bugs">distribution management</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/launchpad/+bugs">any other aspect of Launchpad</a>.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Got an idea for a new feature? Search
            <a href="/launchpad-project/+specs"
            >Blueprint</a> to see if it&#8217;s planned.
            If not,
            write up the summary, and discuss it with us on IRC.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Thanks for helping us make Launchpad a great place to develop software.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
</tal:layout>
